title: Angie Martinez interview
itunes:title: Angie Martinez interview
description:
Today on the show we had legendary radio host Angie Martinez stop by where she spoke about her new show " Untold Stories of Hip- Hop" where she spoke about Snoop Dogg, P Diddy and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to another Florida person, this time they were grandparents because they did not give their grand daughter tomatoes so she retaliated with throwing things back at them and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
